Fix:

```
public static void Transform(ref Vector3 position, ref Matrix matrix, out Vector3 result)
{
    Vector4 v4 = Vector4.Transform( position, matrix );
    float wi = 1.0f / v4.W;
    result.X = v4.X * wi;
    result.Y = v4.Y * wi;
    result.Z = v4.Z * wi;
}
```

